# CampusWash — Spec v10 (V1 Launch)
> Single source of truth. Paste this at the start of every vibe coding session.

---

## What we are building

A college-only clothes platform for CIT Chennai students with 3 modules:
1. **Borrow & Lend** — post clothes to lend, request a borrow, approve/reject/return
2. **Item Request Board** — post "I need X", others respond, requester marks fulfilled
3. **Lost & Found** — post lost or found clothes with a photo, browse and claim

---

## Rules

- CIT Chennai students only — @citchennai.net Google accounts
- No anonymous posting — every user is identified
- No payments — platform is free to use
- No Docker
- Free tier only

