## Auth flow

```
1. Student clicks "Sign in with Google"
2. Firebase popup — only @citchennai.net accounts allowed
3. Frontend sends Firebase ID token to POST /auth/firebase-login
4. Backend verifies token, checks domain, creates user if new,
   parses department + batch year from email, returns JWT
5. If profile_complete = false → redirect to CompleteProfile
6. If profile_complete = true → redirect to Dashboard
```

Email parsing:
```
vijayrajs.aids2024@citchennai.net
→ department: AI&DS
→ batch_year: 2024-2028
```

