### Auth

```
POST /auth/firebase-login
  body:     { firebase_token }
  response: { access_token, user_id, profile_complete, parsed: {department, batch_year} }
  flow:     verify firebase token → check @citchennai.net domain
            → create user if new → return JWT

POST /auth/complete-profile
  auth:     JWT (profile_complete can be false)
  body:     { name, register_number, department, batch_year, phone? }
  response: { message, access_token }
  note:     register_number mandatory, unique, min 6 chars, no spaces

GET /auth/me
  auth:     JWT
  response: { id, email, name, register_number, department,
              batch_year, phone, profile_complete, role }
```

