### Borrow & Lend

```
GET    /borrow/listings              — no auth, paginated, ?type=&size=&page=
POST   /borrow/listings              — JWT, multipart (image optional)
DELETE /borrow/listings/{id}         — JWT, owner only, cannot delete if borrowed
GET    /borrow/listings/{id}         — no auth
POST   /borrow/listings/{id}/request — JWT, not owner, body: {reason,borrow_from,borrow_until}
                                       check: borrow_until - borrow_from <= max_borrow_days
                                       check: no overlapping approved request → BORROW_CONFLICT
GET    /borrow/my-requests           — JWT, paginated
GET    /borrow/my-listings-requests  — JWT, paginated (incoming requests on my listings)
PATCH  /borrow/requests/{id}/approve — JWT, listing owner only
                                       → listing status = borrowed
PATCH  /borrow/requests/{id}/reject  — JWT, listing owner only
PATCH  /borrow/requests/{id}/return  — JWT, listing owner only
                                       → listing status = available
                                       → request status = returned
```

