## Supabase Realtime

Used in frontend only. No backend changes needed.

| Table | Event | Hook |
|---|---|---|
| borrow_requests | UPDATE | useBorrow.js |
| lost_items | UPDATE | useItems.js |
| found_items | UPDATE | useItems.js |
| wrong_deliveries | UPDATE | useWrongDeliveries.js |

Pattern — always clean up:
```javascript
useEffect(() => {
  const channel = supabase
    .channel('borrow_updates')
    .on('postgres_changes',
      { event: 'UPDATE', schema: 'public', table: 'borrow_requests' },
      (payload) => { /* update local state */ }
    )
    .subscribe()
  return () => supabase.removeChannel(channel)
}, [])
```

